        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p><strong>PawfectMatch</strong> is a pet adoption platform dedicated to helping animals find their forever homes. We connect loving individuals with pets from shelters and foster homes, making adoption easy, meaningful, and accessible. Whether you’re searching for a playful pup or a cuddly cat, PawfectMatch helps you find the perfect companion—because every paw deserves a match. ❤️</p>
        <p>We aim to make pet adoption more personal, transparent, and compassionate. Our mission is to: Reduce the number of homeless animals, Support animal shelters and foster networks, Make it easier for people to find pets that truly fit their lifestyle.</p>
